latestPosts.caption:
*READ CAPTION* People are either MATCHA PAGLUS or it’s just GHAAS ka juice for them, there’s no inbetween😂 Which one are you?😜

I was never into matcha until I acquired it’s taste, alot of you might roast me for saying this, but I’ve reallyyyy started loving it 😍

1. Cult by Trio- Firstly, it’s a drivethru place, there’s no seating. I tried Strawberry & Matcha Latte in coconut milk, both were reallyyyy good. Matcha ka waste was not too overpowering, as a first-timer, I think you’ll love it😍 10/10

2. Matcha Vibes- Ughh paid like ₹1200/- for this & got strawberry cream foam in it. It was average, 6/10

3. Maison Chacha- DON’T WASTE YOUR MONEY. Located at a v central location ‘Downtown’ tried 2 diff matchas, both were bheeehh🤮 -2

4. Knot: Aman is an Americano lover & matcha hater, if he LOVED it, I promise you’ll like it as well. Hands down the BESTTT matcha I’ve ever tried in my life. While writing, I’m planning to go here tomorrow morning 😋 100/10❤️

Have you tried any of these?🤔
And what other places should I try next? 🍵😋
